### Health Check
GET http://localhost:7860/health

### Reset
POST http://localhost:7860/reset?session_id=test123

### Step 1 - Escalate P1
POST http://localhost:7860/step?session_id=test123
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "action": "escalate",
    "patient_id": "P1",
    "notes": "critical vitals"
}

### Step 2 - Discharge P2
POST http://localhost:7860/step?session_id=test123
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "action": "discharge",
    "patient_id": "P2",
    "notes": "stable patient"
}

### Step 3 - Treat P3
POST http://localhost:7860/step?session_id=test123
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "action": "treat",
    "patient_id": "P3",
    "notes": "moderate risk"
}

### Predict
POST http://localhost:7860/predict
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "age": 60,
    "heart_rate": 120,
    "oxygen_saturation": 88,
    "systolic_bp": 80,
    "diastolic_bp": 50,
    "temperature": 37.2,
    "symptoms": ["chest pain"],
    "chief_complaint": "chest pain"
}